item.title: HELP .. My Server! PortForward PROB!
item.dc:creator: @Cyph Cyph
item.description:
@Cyph wrote:

Hey, Port Forwarding is a big problem. Many different combinations can arrange from Admin/password to Admin/Admin. Your information/instructions from your router box will always provide you with your username and password. Even though you can port forward, Dont get too excited. Recent routers (I know mostly netgear) have made it where you need a new router if you want to port forward.
